Static Bearer header plumbing (env-only).

Adds OPENCODE_SERVER_BEARER: when set, client-side ServerAuth.header()
emits `Bearer <token>` instead of Basic auth. Server-side opencode does
NOT validate the Bearer; deployments pair this with a JWT-validating
reverse proxy. kfactory itself uses the cache-file flow layered on top
by opencode-kfactory-refresh.patch; the env var is the minimal generic
seam (and the test seam for nix/unit/opencode/tui-attach-smoke.test.ts).

